个基准大概就是：Will Smith eating dreadlocks of a guy eating spaghetti。不如你也用这个 prompt 去试试视频生成大模型现在的真实水平吧。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="503424350" data-ratio="0.9027777777777778" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW94BGEbR6nAvoxMfyI2pykX9yWSdkwGL4ClhJAVq2XaTQAFbvmoEj80e15BiaSI2biavibJTvkSKicvjw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">参考链接：</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">https://twitter.com/GaryMarcus/status/1759578135665004683</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">https://twitter.com/LucaFedeli2/status/1759683824022143222</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">https://twitter.com/Hot_Takes10/status/1758314807252459542</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><em><span style="font-size: 12px;">https://openai.com/sora</span></em></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="578" d